ğŸ“Š Sentiment Analyzer using DistilBERT and Gradio
A web-based sentiment analysis tool built with Python, Gradio, Hugging Face Transformers, and Matplotlib.

DEPLOYMENT LINK - https://purvabhong01-sentimentanalyzer.hf.space/

Users can upload an Excel file (.xls/.xlsx) containing reviews, and the app will:
1. Classify each review as Positive or Negative
2. Display results in a tabular format
3. Generate a Pie Chart of overall sentiment distribution

